description:
➤ Heroes of Faith Series - https://www.amazingfacts.org/media-library/watch/archives/o/1169/t/heroes-of-faith

From the capital city of Michigan, Pastor Doug Batchelor has just completed his 10-part series Heroes of Faith: Stories of Salvation for the Whole Family. 

These messages of hope and revival were broadcast all around the world, and now many thousands have had their faith revived are on fire for the gospel of Jesus Christ. Amazing Facts is praising God that many lives have been changed through the power of the Holy Spirit.
